Package: Rcongas
Type: Package
Title: Copy Number Alterations genotyping from single-cell multiomics 
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Salvatore", "Milite", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="militesalvatore@gmail.com"),
    person("Riccardo", "Bergamin", role=c("aut"), email="riccardo.bergamin@units.it"),
    person("Giulio", "Caravagna", role=c("aut"), email="gcaravagn@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Cancer Data Science Laboratory <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Description: This package is built upon the congas Python package, aiming at the creation of an easy
    frontend to work from R and run the Pyro-based analyis described in congas. The package interfaces 
    with Python through the reticulate package, and contains a number of functions to input and pre-process
    datasets, as well as to visualise and post-process fits.
